{"label":"Word Meanings","id":"word-meaning-4","lockAfter":2,"list":[{"id":"meanings-3","type":"slides2","label":"Word Meanings","commonData":{"title":"Word Meanings","displayType":"custom","autoPlay":false,"substep":false},"data":[{"steps":[[{"type":"title","text":"misery"},"- a state of ill-being due to affliction or misfortune",{"type":"html","text":"Eg: <br><br>\nThe refugee's life was filled with <i><b>misery</b></i> as they struggled to find safety and stability.<br><br>\nShe couldn't hide her <i><b>misery</b></i> when her favorite book was lost."}],[{"type":"title","text":"moisture"},"- wetness caused by water",{"type":"html","text":"Eg: <br><br>\n    The <i><b>moisture</b></i> on the window indicated a humid day.<br><br>\nTo keep the skin hydrated, it's important to use a moisturizer that locks in <i><b>moisture</b></i>."}],[{"type":"title","text":"mural"},"- a painting that is applied to a wall surface",{"type":"html","text":"Eg: <br><br>\nThe artist spent weeks working on a stunning <i><b>mural</b></i> that covered an entire wall of the art gallery.<br><br>\nThe <i><b>mural</b></i> on the side of the building depicted a colorful jungle scene."}],[{"type":"title","text":"mystify"},"- be puzzling or bewildering to",{"type":"html","text":"Eg: <br><br>\n    The magician made the rabbit disappear. It <i><b>mystified</b></i> the audience.<br><br>\nThe cryptic message in the old book continued to <i><b>mystify</b></i> researchers for years."}],[{"type":"title","text":"nectar"},"- a sweet liquid secretion that is attractive to pollinators",{"type":"html","text":"Eg: <br><br>\nThe sweet <i><b>nectar</b></i> of the flowers attracted a variety of colorful butterflies.<br><br>\nThe bees diligently collected <i><b>nectar</b></i> from the blossoms to make honey."}]]},{"steps":[[{"type":"title","text":"observe"},"- watch attentively",{"type":"html","text":"Eg: <br><br>\nBirdwatchers often spend hours in the park to <i><b>observe</b></i> different bird species in their natural habitat.<br><br>\nIt's crucial to <i><b>observe</b></i> safety regulations when using equipment to prevent accidents."}],[{"type":"title","text":"opponent"},"- the opposite team or a person with whom we compete",{"type":"html","text":"Eg: <br><br>\nIn the boxing ring, the determined fighter faced a formidable <i><b>opponent</b></i>.<br><br>\nThe political <i><b>opponent</b></i> delivered a passionate speech in response to the proposed legislation."}],[{"type":"title","text":"ordeal"},"- a severe or trying experience",{"type":"html","text":"Eg: <br><br>\nSurviving a plane crash in the wilderness was a harrowing <i><b>ordeal</b></i> for the passengers.<br><br>\nHe survived the <i><b>ordeal</b></i> and eventually wrote a book about it."}]]},{"steps":[[{"type":"title","text":"origin"},"- the place where something begins",{"type":"html","text":"Eg: <br><br>\nThe <i><b>origin</b></i> of the ancient artifact was traced back to a lost civilization.<br><br>\nUnderstanding the <i><b>origin</b></i> of a word can provide insight into its meaning and usage."}],[{"type":"title","text":"outcome"},"- something that results",{"type":"html","text":"Eg: <br><br>\nThe <i><b>outcome</b></i> of the negotiation was a mutually beneficial agreement for both parties.<br><br>\nThe success of a project often depends on the effort put into achieving a favorable <i><b>outcome</b></i>."}],[{"type":"title","text":"pastime"},"- an interest or pursuit that someone pursues regularly",{"type":"html","text":"Eg: <br><br>\nReading is a beloved <i><b>pastime</b></i> for many people, allowing them to escape into different worlds.<br><br>\nPlaying board games is a popular <i><b>pastime</b></i> for families, promoting quality time together."}],[{"type":"title","text":"pause"},"- cease an action temporarily",{"type":"html","text":"Eg: <br><br>\nThe music conductor signaled for a brief <i><b>pause</b></i> before the orchestra continued playing.<br><br>\nTake a moment to <i><b>pause</b></i> and reflect on your goals before making a decision."}]]},{"steps":[[{"type":"title","text":"perform"},"- get done",{"type":"html","text":"Eg: <br><br>\nThe talented musician was set to <i><b>perform</b></i> a concert in front of a large audience.<br><br>\nThe surgical team worked tirelessly to <i><b>perform</b></i> a life-saving operation."}],[{"type":"title","text":"plunge"},"- dash violently or with great speed or impetuosity",{"type":"html","text":"Eg: <br><br>\nThe thrill-seekers decided to <i><b>plunge</b></i> into the icy waters of the mountain lake.<br><br>\nThe village girls are not afraid to <i><b>plunge</b></i> into the well. They are great swimmers."}],[{"type":"title","text":"predator"},"- any animal that lives by preying on other animals",{"type":"html","text":"Eg: <br><br>\nLions are known as fierce <i><b>predators</b></i> in the African savanna, hunting for their prey.<br><br>\nThe bird of prey is a skilled <i><b>predator</b></i>, soaring high in the sky in search of small animals."}],[{"type":"title","text":"predict"},"- say what happens in the future",{"type":"html","text":"Eg: <br><br>\nMeteorologists use advanced technology to <i><b>predict</b></i> the weather, helping people prepare for storms.<br><br>\nExperts try to <i><b>predict</b></i> the economic trends based on various factors and data."}],[{"type":"title","text":"prevent"},"- stop something from happening",{"type":"html","text":"Eg: <br><br>\nRegular exercise and a healthy diet can help <i><b>prevent</b></i> many common health issues.<br><br>\nThe security measures in place are designed to <i><b>prevent</b></i> unauthorized access to the building."}]]},{"steps":[[{"type":"title","text":"primary"},"- important",{"type":"html","text":"Eg: <br><br>\nEducation is a <i><b>primary</b></i> focus in a child's development, setting the foundation for future success.<br><br>\nThe <i><b>primary</b></i> goal of the project was to reduce carbon emissions and promote sustainability."}],[{"type":"title","text":"privilege"},"- an advantage enjoyed by somebody",{"type":"html","text":"Eg: <br><br>\nHaving access to quality education is a <i><b>privilege</b></i> that not everyone in the world enjoys.<br><br>\nBeing able to travel and explore new cultures is a <i><b>privilege</b></i> that broadens one's perspective."}],[{"type":"title","text":"process"},"- a step by step action",{"type":"html","text":"Eg: <br><br>\nThe manufacturing <i><b>process</b></i> involves multiple stages, from design to production.<br><br>\nCooking a meal requires following a specific <i><b>process</b></i> of chopping, seasoning, and cooking."}],[{"type":"title","text":"rare"},"- difficult to find",{"type":"html","text":"Eg: <br><br>\nThe <i><b>rare</b></i> gemstone found in the cave was one of the most valuable discoveries in years.<br><br>\nA <i><b>rare</b></i> astronomical event, like a solar eclipse, is a captivating sight."}],[{"type":"title","text":"recall"},"- think about a past event",{"type":"html","text":"Eg: <br><br>\nShe struggled to <i><b>recall</b></i> the name of the book she read years ago but could remember the plot.<br><br>\nThe car manufacturer issued a <i><b>recall</b></i> of a certain model due to a safety concern."}]]},{"steps":[[{"type":"title","text":"rely"},"- have confidence or faith in",{"type":"html","text":"Eg: <br><br>\nIn times of need, you can <i><b>rely</b></i> on your close friends to provide support.<br><br>\nBusinesses <i><b>rely</b></i> on customer feedback to improve their products and services."}],[{"type":"title","text":"remark"},"- make or write a comment on",{"type":"html","text":"Eg: <br><br>\nHis <i><b>remark</b></i> during the meeting sparked a thoughtful discussion among the team members.<br><br>\nShe made a humorous <i><b>remark</b></i> that lightened the mood in the room."}],[{"type":"title","text":"resident"},"- someone who lives at a particular place for a long period",{"type":"html","text":"Eg: <br><br>\nThe <i><b>resident</b></i> of the neighborhood organized a community clean-up event to improve the area.<br><br>\nA <i><b>resident</b></i> of the town for over 30 years, he had witnessed many changes over time."}],[{"type":"title","text":"respect"},"- regard highly; think much of",{"type":"html","text":"Eg: <br><br>\nIt's important to <i><b>respect</b></i> other people's opinions and values, even if they differ from your own.<br><br>\nThe teacher earned the <i><b>respect</b></i> of her students through her dedication and fairness."}],[{"type":"title","text":"responsible"},"- worthy of or requiring trust; held accountable",{"type":"html","text":"Eg: <br><br>\nBeing <i><b>responsible</b></i> for a project means taking ownership of its success or failure.<br><br>\nParents must teach their children to be <i><b>responsible</b></i> and accountable for their actions."}],[{"type":"title","text":"reverse"},"- change to the contrary",{"type":"html","text":"Eg: <br><br>\nThe company decided to <i><b>reverse</b></i> its previous decision and rehire the experienced employee.<br><br>\nThe movie's plot took an unexpected <i><b>reverse</b></i> in the final act, surprising the audience."}]]},{"steps":[[{"type":"title","text":"revive"},"- cause to regain consciousness",{"type":"html","text":"Eg: <br><br>\nThe quick administration of CPR helped to <i><b>revive</b></i> the unconscious swimmer at the pool.<br><br>\nA good night's sleep can help you <i><b>revive</b></i> your energy and mental alertness."}],[{"type":"title","text":"risk"},"- a source of danger",{"type":"html","text":"Eg: <br><br>\nInvesting in the stock market carries a certain level of financial <i><b>risk</b></i> due to market fluctuations.<br><br>\nCrossing a busy street without using the crosswalk is a dangerous <i><b>risk</b></i> to one's safety."}],[{"type":"title","text":"scatter"},"- cause to separate and go in different directions",{"type":"html","text":"Eg: <br><br>\nThe strong wind caused the leaves to <i><b>scatter</b></i> in all directions, creating a colorful spectacle.<br><br>\nThe children were told not to <i><b>scatter</b></i> their toys all over the living room."}],[{"type":"title","text":"schedule"},"- a list of times at which things are planned to occur",{"type":"html","text":"Eg: <br><br>\nI have a busy <i><b>schedule</b></i> this week, with meetings and deadlines every day.<br><br>\nThe school's <i><b>schedule</b></i> includes classes in the morning and extracurricular activities in the afternoon."}],[{"type":"title","text":"sensitive"},"- responsive to physical stimuli",{"type":"html","text":"Eg: <br><br>\nSome people have <i><b>sensitive</b></i> skin that may react to certain skincare products.<br><br>\nIt's crucial to be <i><b>sensitive</b></i> to the feelings of others and avoid hurtful comments."}],[{"type":"title","text":"signal"},"- any action or gesture that encodes a message",{"type":"html","text":"Eg: <br><br>\nThe traffic light changed from red to green, giving the <i><b>signal</b></i> for the cars to proceed.<br><br>\nNonverbal <i><b>signals</b></i>, like body language, can convey important messages in a conversation."}],[{"type":"title","text":"solution"},"- a homogeneous mixture of two or more substances",{"type":"html","text":"Eg: <br><br>\nThe scientist worked tirelessly to find a <i><b>solution</b></i> to the environmental problem.<br><br>\nThe <i><b>solution</b></i> to the puzzle required careful thought and creativity."}],[{"type":"title","text":"spoil"},"- make a mess of, destroy or ruin",{"type":"html","text":"Eg: <br><br>\nLeaving food out in the sun can cause it to <i><b>spoil</b></i> quickly, making it unsafe to eat.<br><br>\nIt's important not to <i><b>spoil</b></i> children with excessive gifts, as it may lead to entitlement."}]]}]},{"label":"Fill in the blanks","type":"matchByDragDrop","id":"drag-drop-3","lockAfter":1,"commonData":{"title":"Drag the correct option in each blank to form meaningfull sentences.","fontSize":"1rem"},"data":["The refugee's life was filled with *misery* as they struggled to find safety and stability.\nThe *moisture* on the window indicated a humid day.\nThe artist spent weeks working on a stunning *mural* that covered an entire wall of the art gallery.\nThe magician made the rabbit disappear. It *mystified* the audience.\nThe sweet *nectar* of the flowers attracted a variety of colorful butterflies.","The *origin* of the ancient artifact was traced back to a lost civilization.\nThe *outcome* of the negotiation was a mutually beneficial agreement for both parties.\nReading is a beloved *pastime* for many people, allowing them to escape into different worlds.\nThe music conductor signaled for a brief *pause* before the orchestra continued playing.","The talented musician was set to *perform* a concert in front of a large audience.\nThe thrill-seekers decided to *plunge* into the icy waters of the mountain lake.\nLions are known as fierce *predators* in the African savanna, hunting for their prey.\nMeteorologists use advanced technology to *predict* the weather, helping people prepare for storms.\nRegular exercise and a healthy diet can help *prevent* many common health issues.","Education is a *primary* focus in a child's development, setting the foundation for future success.\nHaving access to quality education is a *privilege* that not everyone in the world enjoys.\nThe manufacturing *process* involves multiple stages, from design to production.\nThe *rare* gemstone found in the cave was one of the most valuable discoveries in years.","She struggled to *recall* the name of the book she read years ago but could remember the plot.\nIn times of need, you can *rely* on your close friends to provide support.\nHis *remark* during the meeting sparked a thoughtful discussion among the team members.\nThe *resident* of the neighborhood organized a community clean-up event to improve the area.\nEIt's important to *respect* other people's opinions and values, even if they differ from your own.","Being *responsible* for a project means taking ownership of its success or failure.\nThe company decided to *reverse* its previous decision and rehire the experienced employee.\nThe quick administration of CPR helped to *revive* the unconscious swimmer at the pool.\nInvesting in the stock market carries a certain level of financial *risk* due to market fluctuations.\nThe strong wind caused the leaves to *scatter* in all directions, creating a colorful spectacle.","I have a busy *schedule* this week, with meetings and deadlines every day.\nSome people have *sensitive* skin that may react to certain skincare products.\nThe traffic light changed from red to green, giving the *signal* for the cars to proceed.\nThe scientist worked tirelessly to find a *solution* to the environmental problem.\nLeaving food out in the sun can cause it to *spoil* quickly, making it unsafe to eat.","Birdwatchers often spend hours in the park to *observe* different bird species in their natural habitat.\nIn the boxing ring, the determined fighter faced a formidable *opponent*.\nSurviving a plane crash in the wilderness was a harrowing *ordeal* for the passengers."]},{"type":"completeWord","id":"complete-word-3","label":"Complete Word","data":["A state of ill-being due to affliction or misfortune | Misery\nWetness caused by water | Moisture\nA painting that is applied to a wall surface | Mural\nBe puzzling or bewildering to | Mystify\nA sweet liquid secretion that is attractive to pollinators | Nectar\nWatch attentively | Observe\nThe opposite team or a person with whom we compete  | Opponent\nA severe or trying experience | Ordeal","The place where something begins | Origin\nSomething that results | Outcome\nAn interest or pursuit that someone pursues regularly | Pastime\nCease an action temporarily | Pause\nGet done | Perform\nDash violently or with great speed or impetuosity | Plunge\nAny animal that lives by preying on other animals | Predator\nSay what happens in the future. | Predict\nStop something from happening | Prevent","Important | Primary\nAn advantage enjoyed by somebody  | Privilege\nA step by step action | Process\nDifficult to find | Rare\nThink about a past event | Recall\nHave confidence or faith in | Rely\nMake or write a comment on | Remark\nSomeone who lives at a particular place for a long period | Resident\nRegard highly; think much of | Respect","Worthy of or requiring trust; held accountable | Responsible\nChange to the contrary | Reverse\nCause to regain consciousness | Revive\nA source of danger | Risk\nCause to separate and go in different directions | Scatter\nA list of times at which things are planned to occur | Schedule\nResponsive to physical stimuli | Sensitive\nAny action or gesture that encodes a message | Signal\nA homogeneous mixture of two or more substances | Solution\nMake a mess of, destroy or ruin | Spoil"]},{"id":"meanings-4","type":"slides2","label":"Word Meanings 2","commonData":{"title":"Word Meanings 2","displayType":"custom","autoPlay":false,"substep":false},"data":[{"steps":[[{"type":"title","text":"starve"},"- die of food deprivation",{"type":"html","text":"Eg: <br><br>\nIn times of famine, people may <i><b>starve</b></i> due to the scarcity of food.<br><br>\nThe decision to <i><b>starve</b></i> themselves in protest drew attention to the hunger strike."}],[{"type":"title","text":"steer"},"- be a guiding or motivating force or drive",{"type":"html","text":"Eg: <br><br>\nParents often <i><b>steer</b></i> their children toward positive life choices through guidance and support.<br><br>\nAs the captain of the ship, he had to <i><b>steer</b></i> the vessel safely through treacherous waters."}],[{"type":"title","text":"struggle"},"- strenuous effort",{"type":"html","text":"Eg: <br><br>\nThe journey to overcome addiction can be a long and challenging <i><b>struggle</b></i>.<br><br>\nDespite the <i><b>struggle</b></i>, they persevered and achieved their goals."}],[{"type":"title","text":"suitable"},"- meant or adapted for an occasion or use",{"type":"html","text":"Eg: <br><br>\nThe formal attire was <i><b>suitable</b></i> for the wedding ceremony, adhering to the dress code.<br><br>\nThe spacious and well-lit room was <i><b>suitable</b></i> for hosting a productive business meeting."}],[{"type":"title","text":"survey"},"- determining opinions by interviewing people",{"type":"html","text":"Eg: <br><br>\nResearchers conducted a <i><b>survey</b></i> to gather opinions from the public on environmental issues.<br><br>\nThe annual customer satisfaction <i><b>survey</b></i> revealed areas for improvement in the company's services."}]]},{"steps":[[{"type":"title","text":"swift"},"- moving very fast",{"type":"html","text":"Eg: <br><br>\nThe <i><b>swift</b></i> response of the firefighters prevented the wildfire from spreading further.<br><br>\nThe cheetah is known for its incredible <i><b>swift</b></i> speed in pursuit of prey."}],[{"type":"title","text":"symbol"},"- something visible that represents something invisible",{"type":"html","text":"Eg: <br><br>\nThe dove is often seen as a <i><b>symbol</b></i> of peace and harmony in many cultures.<br><br>\nThe red heart is a common <i><b>symbol</b></i> of love and affection."}],[{"type":"title","text":"talent"},"- natural abilities or qualities",{"type":"html","text":"Eg: <br><br>\nThe young musician displayed a remarkable <i><b>talent</b></i> for playing the piano, captivating the audience.<br><br>\nHer artistic <i><b>talent</b></i> shone through her beautifully painted landscapes."}],[{"type":"title","text":"theory"},"- a belief that can guide behavior",{"type":"html","text":"Eg: <br><br>\nIn science, a <i><b>theory</b></i> is a well-established explanation that has undergone extensive testing.<br><br>\nThe <i><b>theory</b></i> of relativity, formulated by Albert Einstein, revolutionized the field of physics."}],[{"type":"title","text":"thrill"},"- something that causes a sudden intense feeling",{"type":"html","text":"Eg: <br><br>\nThe roller coaster ride provided an adrenaline-pumping <i><b>thrill</b></i> as it sped down steep drops and sharp turns.<br><br>\nAchieving a long-term goal can bring a deep sense of <i><b>thrill</b></i> and accomplishment."}]]},{"steps":[[{"type":"title","text":"treasure"},"- any possession that is highly valued by its owner",{"type":"html","text":"Eg: <br><br>\nThe pirate legend spoke of hidden <i><b>treasure</b></i> buried on a remote island.<br><br>\nThe old journal contained clues to a lost family <i><b>treasure</b></i> hidden in the attic."}],[{"type":"title","text":"triumph"},"- a successful ending of a struggle or contest",{"type":"html","text":"Eg: <br><br>\nThe athlete's hard work and determination led to a <i><b>triumph</b></i> in the championship race.<br><br>\nThe successful launch of the spacecraft was a <i><b>triumph</b></i> for the entire space agency."}],[{"type":"title","text":"value"},"- the quality that renders something desirable",{"type":"html","text":"Eg: <br><br>\nHonesty and integrity are qualities highly <i><b>valued</b></i> in both personal and professional relationships.<br><br>\nThe antique vase had great <i><b>value</b></i> due to its historical significance and craftsmanship."}],[{"type":"title","text":"vision"},"- the ability to see",{"type":"html","text":"Eg: <br><br>\nGood eyesight is essential for clear <i><b>vision</b></i> and the ability to see the world around us.<br><br>\nThe visionary leader had a grand <i><b>vision</b></i> for the future of the company."}],[{"type":"title","text":"volunteer"},"- a person who performs work done by choice",{"type":"html","text":"Eg: <br><br>\nShe decided to <i><b>volunteer</b></i> at the local animal shelter to help care for abandoned pets.<br><br>\nMany <i><b>volunteer</b></i> firefighters responded to the emergency, bravely combating the blaze."}]]},{"steps":[[{"type":"title","text":"wander"},"- move or cause to move in a sinuous or circular course",{"type":"html","text":"Eg: <br><br>\nThe hikers chose to <i><b>wander</b></i> through the forest, exploring its hidden trails and natural beauty.<br><br>\nWhen you <i><b>wander</b></i> through the city streets, you may stumble upon charming shops and cafes."}],[{"type":"title","text":"wisdom"},"- accumulated knowledge or erudition or enlightenment",{"type":"html","text":"Eg: <br><br>\nWith age comes <i><b>wisdom</b></i>, as life experiences teach valuable lessons.<br><br>\nSeeking advice from someone with <i><b>wisdom</b></i> can provide guidance in making important decisions."}],[{"type":"title","text":"wit"},"- mental ability",{"type":"html","text":"Eg: <br><br>\nHer quick <i><b>wit</b></i> and sense of humor made her the life of the party.<br><br>\nThe stand-up comedian's clever <i><b>wit</b></i> had the audience in stitches."}],[{"type":"title","text":"woe"},"- misery resulting from affliction",{"type":"html","text":"Eg: <br><br>\nThe loss of a loved one brought deep <i><b>woe</b></i> and sorrow to the grieving family.<br><br>\nEconomic <i><b>woe</b></i> can result from financial instability and market downturns."}]]}]},{"label":"Fill in the blanks","type":"matchByDragDrop","id":"drag-drop-4","lockAfter":1,"commonData":{"title":"Drag the correct option in each blank to form meaningfull sentences.","fontSize":"1rem"},"data":["In times of famine, people may *starve* due to the scarcity of food.\nParents often *steer* their children toward positive life choices through guidance and support.\nThe journey to overcome addiction can be a long and challenging *struggle*.\nThe formal attire was *suitable* for the wedding ceremony, adhering to the dress code.\nResearchers conducted a *survey* to gather opinions from the public on environmental issues.","The *swift* response of the firefighters prevented the wildfire from spreading further.\nThe dove is often seen as a *symbol* of peace and harmony in many cultures.\nThe young musician displayed a remarkable *talent* for playing the piano, captivating the audience.\nIn science, a *theory* is a well-established explanation that has undergone extensive testing.\nThe roller coaster ride provided an adrenaline-pumping *thrill* as it sped down steep drops and sharp turns.","The pirate legend spoke of hidden *treasure* buried on a remote island.\nThe athlete's hard work and determination led to a *triumph* in the championship race.\nHonesty and integrity are qualities highly *valued* in both personal and professional relationships.\nGood eyesight is essential for clear *vision* and the ability to see the world around us.\nShe decided to *volunteer* at the local animal shelter to help care for abandoned pets.","The hikers chose to *wander* through the forest, exploring its hidden trails and natural beauty.\nWith age comes *wisdom*, as life experiences teach valuable lessons.\nHer quick *wit* and sense of humor made her the life of the party.\nThe loss of a loved one brought deep *woe* and sorrow to the grieving family."]},{"type":"completeWord","id":"complete-word-4","label":"Complete Word","data":["Die of food deprivation | Starve\nBe a guiding or motivating force or drive | Steer\nStrenuous effort | Struggle\nMeant or adapted for an occasion or use | Suitable\nDetermining opinions by interviewing people | Survey\nMoving very fast | Swift\nSomething visible that represents something invisible | Symbol\nNatural abilities or qualities | Talent\nA belief that can guide behavior | Theory\nSomething that causes a sudden intense feeling | Thrill","Any possession that is highly valued by its owner | Treasure\nA successful ending of a struggle or contest | Triumph\nThe quality that renders something desirable | Value\nThe ability to see | Vision\nA person who performs work done by choice | Volunteer\nMove or cause to move in a sinuous or circular course | Wander\nAccumulated knowledge or erudition or enlightenment | Wisdom\nMental ability | Wit\nMisery resulting from affliction | Woe"]}]}